## Apple Intelligence OpenAI API Environment Variables

## Server Binding
# APPLE_AI_HOST=0.0.0.0  # Use 127.0.0.1 to restrict access to local machine only
# APPLE_AI_PORT=8002

## Performance & Limits
# APPLE_AI_MAX_CONCURRENCY=4
# APPLE_AI_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=30.0

## Authentication (Optional)
# APPLE_AI_API_KEY=your-secret-key-here

## Debug mode
# APPLE_AI_DEBUG_PAYLOAD=false

## Strip system prompt from Coding IDE, like Opencode
# APPLE_AI_STRIP_SYSTEM_PROMPT=false

## The following is only useful when APPLE_AI_STRIP_SYSTEM_PROMPT=true
# APPLE_AI_CUSTOM_SYSTEM_PROMPT="You are a helpful coding assistant."

